devdoc.title: Maintains a sorted list of unsigned ints keyed by address.

contains(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.List.notice: Returns whether or not a particular key is present in the sorted list.

getElements(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.L.notice: Gets all elements from the doubly linked list.

getHead(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.List.notice: Returns the key of the first element in the list.

getMedian(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.Lis.notice: Returns the key of the median element in the list.

getMedianValue(SortedLinkedListWithMedia.notice: Returns the median value of the sorted list.

getNumElements(SortedLinkedListWithMedia.notice: Returns the number of elements in the list.

getTail(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.List.notice: Returns the key of the last element in the list.

getValue(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.List.notice: Returns the value for a particular key in the sorted list.

insert(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.List s.notice: Inserts an element into a doubly linked list.

remove(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.List s.notice: Removes an element from the doubly linked list.

update(SortedLinkedListWithMedian.List s.notice: Updates an element in the list.
